---
title: "How to Use AI to Build a Support Knowledge Base That Gets Smarter Over Time"
date: "2026-01-13"
summary: "Build a support knowledge base that improves with every resolved ticket. Use AI to turn your team's experience into a growing asset."
coverImage: ""
tags:
